hikMemoryUsage.description: the Usage of hikvision products Memory, value scope is (0-100)
hikMemoryUsage.name: hikMemoryUsage

hikDiskFreeSpace.description: the size of local disk entry free space, if we get 100, means free space is 100M
hikDiskFreeSpace.name: hikDiskFreeSpace

hikCPUNum.description: the number of hikvision products cpu
hikCPUNum.name: hikCPUNum

hikDiskCapability.description: the size of local disk entry all space, if we get 100, means all space is 100M
hikDiskCapability.name: hikDiskCapability

hikEntityIndex.description: hikvision device unique index, for DVR this is serial NO.
hikEntityIndex.name: hikEntityIndex

hikCPUFrequency.description: the frequency of hikvision products cpu, format like 2000MHZ
hikCPUFrequency.name: hikCPUFrequency

hikDiskIndex.description: An unique value for each local disk entry. Its value ranges between 1 and the value of ifNumber.
hikDiskIndex.name: hikDiskIndex

hikDiskVolume.description: A textual string containing information about local disk
hikDiskVolume.name: hikDiskVolume

hikDiskTable.description: A list of disk entries. The number of entries is given by the value of hikDiskNum.
hikDiskTable.name: hikDiskTable

hikDiskNum.description: the number of hikvision device local disks
hikDiskNum.name: hikDiskNum

hikObjectID.description: display hikvision product object ID, now dvr do not need this will return 0
hikObjectID.name: hikObjectID

hikPort.description: hikvision device valid manager port,default is 8000
hikPort.name: hikPort

hikDiskEntry.description: A disk entry containing objects at local disk status.
hikDiskEntry.name: hikDiskEntry

hikService.description: display hikvision product service type, now dvr will return Unknown
hikService.name: hikService

hikCMSDefType.description: display hikvision product defined CMS type, now dvr will return Unknown
hikCMSDefType.name: hikCMSDefType

hikTrapHostIp1.description: display hikvision product 1st trap host ip address
hikTrapHostIp1.name: hikTrapHostIp1

hikObjectName.description: display hikvision product object Name, now dvr do not need this will return nothing
hikObjectName.name: hikObjectName
